Natural-Language-Toolkit for bahasa Malaysia, powered by Deep Learning.

Malaya support:

* Entities Recognition
* Language Detection
* Normalizer
* Num2Word
* Part-of-Speech Recognition
* Sentiment Analysis
* Spell Correction
* Stemmer
* Summarization
* Topic Modelling
* Topic and Influencers Analysis
* Toxicity Analysis
* Word2Vec

Malaya fully utilised Github Wiki, you can read more about `Malaya Wiki <https://github.com/DevconX/Malaya/wiki>`__
